Tigenix to Get 4.95 Million-Euro Loan for Crohn’s Fistula Study

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-10-03T05:07:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/tigenix-to-get-4-95-million-euro-loan-for-crohn-s-fistula-study.html
TiGenix NV (TIG) ’s Cellerix unit will get a
4.95 million-euro loan from the “Madrid Network” to finance
the company’s phase III study for complex perianal fistulas in
Crohn’s disease patients, TiGenix said today in an e-mailed
statement.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Clapham at 
 aclapham@bloomberg.net  